    <h1>What <span class="accent">100 Grams of Protein</span> Actually Looks Like<br>for Men Over 40</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Most men over 40 are eating 60–80g of protein a day without knowing it. Here's what 100 grams actually looks like — and why it's the right place to start.</p>
